skdetail:

Invocation Name: social science test
des:
Answer questions across History, Geography and Environmental Sciences and know where you stand with respect to your social science knowledge. 

Ask Alexa to start the quiz. You will be asked 15 questions in a mixed bag trivia. Get all fifteen right to earn a position in the leaderboard. And if you get any wrong, just ask for a review to learn about your mistakes.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
